Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:46.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\fscx105\fs80\fnMailart Rubberstamp\c&H7A8995&\pos(640,458)}Wolf and a New Journey
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought our next meeting would be a tearful reunion. What a miserable sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They set us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the only thing I could protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,God, you're a fine fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Face swollen from being beaten,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,covered in dirt, wrists burned by rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you endure such humiliation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole time you're protecting my neatly folded cloak from the rain like your life depends on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're softhearted beyond belief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be about to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was best to follow the plan and resume our journey as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so I opted not to fight those pups and took a more civilized approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that they made you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is what I get in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To accept what's happened to you is entirely beyond me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find Lemerio and give him what he deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to take care of Liebert as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you have a good reason for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to kill Norah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is with her partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably be all right in any case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Partner? Sheep dogs can only do so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You could...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I could what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You could fight a hundred armed men without breaking a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in my wolf form, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And that little girl is a shepherd!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so... could you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,An innocent person is about to die, and I can't just look the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll reward you handsomely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to grant any wish as long as you don't ask for Norah's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can stop this but you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I should take my clothes off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a shame to waste the time someone put into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't guarantee the life of anyone who annoys me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you will if that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly have found yourself a way with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What a troublesome companion I've acquired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, isn't there something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a magnificent tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a little forced, but it'll do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now close your eyes for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, hop on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hold on to my fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to carry you in my mouth if you fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold on for dear life—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I really detest shepherds, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Norah's going to quit working as a shepherd regardless of whether this plan succeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided on what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The finest peach preserves that money can buy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just don't bankru—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san} and {*}Miss Holo{*Holo-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When we found them, it was already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We found them lying on top of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Norah{*Norah-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I understand how terrible this must be for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to pull ourselves together and fight to the end as those who survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We've caught up to them already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those bastards are well-armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There are around twenty of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That many?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. Leave it all to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to lay low after I leap over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump off when I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the shepherd and the sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Norah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She was safe after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the shepherd and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shepherd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Enek...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you three hundred Lumione if you protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Enek!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Enek!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Norah{*Norah-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a ghost, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me reveal the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That wolf is Holo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss... Holo{*Holo... san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to swallow him whole, but the gold he was carrying would have upset my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fiends! Do you think you're going to get away with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day, {*}Mr. Liebert{*Liebert-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't the one who betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me... I didn't... I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This wolf has been summoned as a messenger of the one and only God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies will do you no good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The cut you asked for was too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If we went along, we'd only be able to pay off our debts without making a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Lemerio asked me to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both merchants, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bring me down to your level!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's... okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Long story short, Lemerio Trading betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They were planning to kill you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling something wasn't right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run away with the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.02,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have six hundred Lumione worth of gold even without having to resort to smuggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ignore those traitors at Lemerio Trading and split the gold amongst ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have enough to live in luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, we wouldn't have been able to buy the gold without their contribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If we run away with the gold, they'll go bankrupt and end up on the streets with certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have to live our lives after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be an end to this grudge if we take revenge for their betrayal.{If we avenge this betrayal by ruining them, then we can be sure someone will one day come seeking revenge on us.}{i understood this as written}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't say you'll kill every last one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:12:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want the bread I buy tomorrow to have been paid for in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many ways to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to make a decision that'll lead to a brighter future?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo, if it weren't for you, I'd be freezing to death by the forest right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you my gratitude for listening to my selfish request.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my travel companion is tiresome beyond words!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest we do the following.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Might I hear the truth now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.19,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,There's a limit to how generous a person can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:53.37,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,You can decide whether you want to carry this gold into Lubinheigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.82,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,You could also settle for your fair share of this gold right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.21,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:04.13,Default,,1,1,0,,But if we can manage to smuggle it safely, its value will\Nincrease to six thousand Lumione through my connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Six thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We could save Lemerio Trading with that kind of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't hide anything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't enough gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Six hundred Lumione was more than an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hundred at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:26.86,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,If you split the gold up, there wouldn't have been anything left after you paid your debt back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.49,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,You would have had to carry out the smuggling to make a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.57,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,Lemerio was in a desperate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:37.95,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,They only managed to get one-sixth of the amount we had agreed upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:43.79,Default,TLC,1,1,0,,Once they got it inside, they probably could have gotten a thousand Lumione at most...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:49.43,Default,TLC,1,1,0,,...so they knew they wouldn't have enough to pay for our silence from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:54.68,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,It's probably why they agreed to our offer in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I understand the circumstances, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anything else bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to lie like that for her sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I being a showoff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to shoulder the burden by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have other things on my mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to find Lemerio, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you coming with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Matters of business don't concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to fall off if you don't hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Five hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we succeed in smuggling the gold in,\Nwe'd like you to buy it for five hundred Lumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Absolutely not. Do you really think we have the funds to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you to pay in full right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign a contract that will accommodate a gradual repayment of your debt within a period of ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Five hundred is still out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who created a trading company that had the most impressive dock in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Five hundred Lumione in ten years must be child's play to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard everything from {*}Mr. Liebert{*Liebert-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of running away with a paltry amount of money,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's in your best interests to concede to our demands and attempt to revive your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The bearer of the deed will be the Lohen Trading Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The union?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be able to betray a private trader like myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but you won't be able to get away with doing the same thing to a trading union.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd never see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for making me worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You son of a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you call filial devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:17.08,Default,TLC,1,1,0,,So now you just sell this ten year contract to me and never have to deal with Lemerio again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a simple gold transaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't tell you about the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll buy it for thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay an extra hundred if your deal goes through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a cheerful mood. Think of it as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:41.68,Default,,1,1,0,,That should be enough for me to cover all the apologies\Nand such I'll need to be making as well as my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have become a full-fledged merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drink until we pass out as soon as I'm finished with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not sure I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My companion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. What is it that you wanted to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First, how much trust do you have in that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can catch up to Norah if she tries to run away with the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hand her the gold out of blind faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your next question?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll answer anything you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you at least that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,want to get some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose name did you call when I confronted the girl and the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't hear anything because I was caught up in the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure you called out someone's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it been eating at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I called out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You just lied, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have called out to you if I take the circumstances into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a critical situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt I would have instinctively chosen to call your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name isn't as long as hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I'd said "Norah," it still would have been distinct even if I said it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, I could have said Holo in less than a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's entirely plausible that you could miss it if you were distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Pretty convincing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You called out my name because it isn't as long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What upsets me even more is the fact that you sincerely believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have scratched you up to my heart's content if you had said you called out to that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Call out my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is easy to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He was never in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He had just realized what I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a wonderful partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Much more useful than this man over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you two find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:20.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(100,300)\3c&H000000&}I found myself lost and alone on this journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:28.44,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(100,300)\3c&H000000&}Though my heart wandered far and wide, I could move not an inch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:36.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(100,300)\3c&H000000&}But now I can depart for any distant land
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:45.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(100,300)\3c&H000000&}Now that we've met on this road
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:53.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(100,300)\3c&H000000&}Even the unfamiliar songs of travelers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:23:03.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(100,300)\3c&H000000&}Can spark nostalgia in me when I'm with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.88,0:23:12.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur1\3c&H000000&}If I could take your outstretched hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:20.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur1\3c&H000000&}Then how far could we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:29.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur1\3c&H000000&}Let's set off to wherever we please
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:38.64,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur1\3c&H000000&}And bask in the sounds and smells of unfamiliar lands
